-  #ls -l /root/dir1/test1
- -rw-r--r--. it just raw file in linux there is nothing mentioned in front of rw it just - so its raw file
- #ls -ld /root/dir1/
- drwxrwxrwt. it is a dir so will see the first letter is **d**rwxrwxrwt
- #ls -l /root/dir1/
- lrwxrwxrwt. it is a link file soft hard  so will see the first letter is **l**rwxrwxrwt
- #ls -l /dev/vbd/
- brwxrwx---. it is block file media files like external drives (pen drive )
- #tty
- terminal file one user can connect multiple time multiple user can connect multiple time
- #ls -l /dev/pts/1
- crw--w-----. Caracter file
- r d l b cls socket file pipefile
